subject: Some AM linear scan voices form tonight
author: Frank Sumption
full_text:
These are from #24, I think it beats every earlier box hands down.  
 There is one that seems to be a warning aobut Osama, and beng "Ready 
in London".

 The one about the "Cabbage people" is a head scratcher, clear but I 
have no idea what that means.  

 This isn't the whole session, just a quick scan through, I also didn't 
have the line out plugged into the deck's line in, I hit the earphone 
jack by mistake, so this session is recorded directly from the speaker, 
something that can't be done very well on earlier models because of 
lack of volume. 

 Frank-S
